1. *Tijelo* je stvoreno da uživa. (The body is created to enjoy.)
2. On je posjedovao čvrsto *tijelo*. (He possessed a strong body.)
3. Pokušao je da štiti *tijelo* od zaraze. (He tried to protect the body from infection.)
4. Njegovo *tijelo* je bilo prekriveno ranama. (His body was covered with wounds.)
5. Ona je čuvala svoje *tijelo* od sunca. (She was protecting her body from the sun.)
6. *Tijela* su prošla kroz nezamislive muke. (The bodies went through unimaginable sufferings.)